OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK is falling behind in protecting 
OL,6, workers from artificial intelligence   
OL,7, (AI), a trade union has warned.        
OL,9,FThe TUC said the UK had no plans, like 
OL,10,Fthe EU's AI Act, to regulate its use in
OL,11,Fhiring, firing and setting work        
OL,12,Fconditions. The union has asked a      
OL,13,Ftaskforce to draft legal protections.  
OL,15,FThe government said it was committed to
OL,16,Fimproving and upholding worker rights. 
OL,18,FIt comes as the boss of Octopus Energy 
OL,19,Ftold the BBC its customers prefer      
OL,20,Femails written by AI over his staff.   
